label: __init__

def __init__(self,
                 logger,
                 context_qualifiers: dict | None = None,
                 repo_root: str | None = None,  
                 use_unicode=False,
                 use_regex=False, 
                 strict=False):
        self.logger = logger
        self.context_qualifiers = context_qualifiers
        self.repo_root = repo_root
        self.use_unicode = use_unicode
        self.use_regex = use_regex
        self.strict = strict
